cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

This paper deals with generating and manipulating facial images using high-level semantic attributes, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The proposed model involves formulating a new space for learning relationships between attributes and RGB imagery, which also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper presents an iterative training algorithm, which falls under graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
